description:
This document provides an outline for the study protocol carried under WP2 of the OBO2 project (https://www.rivm.nl/bestrijdingsmiddelen/onderzoek-bestrijdingsmiddelen-en-omwonenden/werkpakket-2).&nbsp; 
 The study protocol can also serve as a fieldwork manual for performing similiar research in other EU countries. It is highly recommended however to check if the study design can be used in the specific country of interest. 
 This is version 2 (v2) of the protocol and its deliverable 2.1 from the OBO2 project.

